  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The proposed study will assess the ability of a naturally occurring sugar to improve the
      function of arteries with age. Overall, the proposed research project has the long-term
      potential to influence clinical practice guidelines by establishing a novel, easy to deliver,
      cost-effective therapy for treating age-associated arterial dysfunction and reducing the risk
      of cardiovascular disease with age.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
